GSD.description:
octeontx2-pf: Fix resource leakage in VF driver unbind

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.1.7 by commit c8ca0ad10df08ea36bcac1288062d567d22604c9, it was introduced in version v5.15 by commit 2da48943274712fc3204089d9a97078350765635. For more details please see the references link.
